        "username": "ablagodarenko"
      },
      "date": "2014-12-29 11:58:40.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAndreas wrote: Artem, thanks for the patch. We're not planning to land any patches for b2_6, since that is not a maintenance branch. Is this patch needed for b2_5 or master?\n\nBecause of no possibility to land to b2_6 I have ported the patch to master. We can abandon this patch now.",
